WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:02.747
Previously on "Us"...

00:02.750 --> 00:05.778
- What?
- Just imagine a montage.

00:05.781 --> 00:09.113
A group of fine looking grad students

00:09.115 --> 00:11.916
were invited to a secret school for magic

00:11.918 --> 00:13.348
where a bunch of stuff happened

00:13.351 --> 00:14.692
that doesn't really matter,

00:14.695 --> 00:17.889
until they ran into a mysterious figure.

00:17.891 --> 00:20.684
The answer to a riddle they
didn't even know to ask.

00:20.687 --> 00:21.926
It's you.

00:21.928 --> 00:23.461
Do you want this recap or not?

00:23.463 --> 00:27.265
So yeah, it was me. Things were awesome.

00:27.267 --> 00:29.934
For a minute. We became kings and queens.

00:29.936 --> 00:32.103
Well, everybody but you.

00:32.104 --> 00:35.890
Everyone hooked up, I had a
threesome with two harpies.

00:35.893 --> 00:38.408
Just get to the parts about me.

00:38.411 --> 00:41.546
You had a lot of drama with your hands.

00:41.548 --> 00:44.682
You signed a billion-year
contract with the Library

00:44.684 --> 00:47.952
- to help out Kady.
- Wait, who's that?

00:47.954 --> 00:51.046
Kady Orloff-Diaz? Love of your life?

00:51.049 --> 00:52.731
Looks like she could
crack open your balls,

00:52.734 --> 00:54.225
because she can?

00:54.227 --> 00:57.085
Well, it was a love for the ages.

00:57.088 --> 01:00.231
Despite the fact that Kady
got in way over her head

01:00.233 --> 01:02.367
with some hedge witches.
Especially her best bitch,

01:02.369 --> 01:04.468
Julia Wicker. Their term, not mine.

01:04.471 --> 01:07.405
I would never. Whatever went down

01:07.407 --> 01:10.408
definitely made them ex-best...

01:10.410 --> 01:12.276
Witches. Truthfully,

01:12.278 --> 01:14.245
the only person Kady can stand is you.

01:14.247 --> 01:16.481
And that pretty much cut both ways.

01:16.483 --> 01:18.616
No, come on, Penny,
don't... don't... Come on.

01:18.618 --> 01:21.285
And then you died. Kind of.

01:21.287 --> 01:25.656
Meanwhile, magic got all jacked up.

01:25.658 --> 01:28.226
You know what's weird,
that jacked up is bad,

01:28.228 --> 01:32.363
- but jacked off is great.
- Focus, dude.

01:32.365 --> 01:35.333
So, with magic gone,
a bunch of Fairy dicks

01:35.335 --> 01:38.636
invaded Fillory, made Eliot
and Margo look like derps,

01:38.638 --> 01:41.506
so the people revolted. Only ray of hope?

01:41.508 --> 01:43.965
Julia mysteriously still has magic.

01:43.968 --> 01:46.077
Why? Question mark!

01:46.079 --> 01:47.828
We got sent on a dope quest

01:47.831 --> 01:50.647
to find the Seven Keys that unlock magic.

01:50.650 --> 01:52.517
But the fourth one got dragon gobbled

01:52.519 --> 01:54.218
and lost in the Underworld.

01:54.220 --> 01:56.053
The other Penny sent us the key,

01:56.055 --> 01:58.089
but never came back.

01:58.091 --> 02:01.858
- Then came my grand adventure.
- Hard pass.

02:01.861 --> 02:04.762
I also saved the day
in your dumb timeline.

02:04.765 --> 02:07.498
- And snagged up Key seven.
- Yeah, I was there for that.

02:07.500 --> 02:08.906
And you didn't save shit.

02:08.908 --> 02:11.636
Now wait, you skipped the Sixth Key.

02:11.638 --> 02:13.371
This makes no goddamn sense.

02:13.373 --> 02:16.274
No, it's intentionally confusing.

02:16.276 --> 02:19.644
You see, Julia saved a bunch
of Fairies from slavery,

02:19.646 --> 02:22.447
So the Fairy Queen was
like, I have the Sixth Key,

02:22.449 --> 02:25.216
but I'm not going to give
it to you because she's...

02:25.218 --> 02:27.618
A creamy bitch is what she is.

02:27.620 --> 02:30.632
Meanwhile, Alice has
been acting real fishy.

02:30.635 --> 02:31.663
Quentin was all like...

02:31.666 --> 02:32.557
Are you working for the Library?

02:32.559 --> 02:34.057
- And she was all...
- Yes.

02:34.060 --> 02:36.127
And now, if you would please refer

02:36.129 --> 02:37.913
to the hookup/murder chart.

02:37.916 --> 02:40.765
Penny got with the other Alice.

02:40.767 --> 02:42.893
- Interesting.
- Now that we know

02:42.896 --> 02:48.138
who porked whom, let's
go over who murdered whom.

02:48.141 --> 02:49.830
Penny.

02:56.683 --> 03:00.084
You're Kady.

03:00.086 --> 03:03.788
- What's going on?
- I'm not your Penny.

